image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a storage area or office basement. In the center is a black three-drawer lateral filing cabinet with yellow sticky notes on each drawer. To the left of the cabinet is a vertical hanging file rack containing numerous large, tan-colored folders or documents. On top of the filing cabinet are several rolled-up documents and a white FedEx Express shipping box. To the right is another black filing cabinet, partially open. In the foreground, a large brown cardboard box is visible. The background shows white walls with some utility fixtures and a metal duct.
